Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.99,0:24:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autumn quietly arrives in Academy City.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.05,0:25:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One promise destroys those peaceful days.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.31,0:25:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's transpiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.85,0:25:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Penalty Game."
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.67,0:25:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
